ItemProposalWizard is a WizardForm
    use for action CreateItemProposalFromWizard
    title is "NewItemProposalInformation"
    summary form is ItemProposalProductSummary
    show steps
    ProposedItemInformation is a Panel
        mouse over text is "PleaseEnterDetailInformationRelatedToTheItemsYouAreProposing;YouMustEnterAtLeastOneUnitOfMeasureToUseForBuying"
        panel header is "PleaseEnterDetailInformationRelatedToTheItemsYouAreProposing;YouMustEnterAtLeastOneUnitOfMeasureToUseForBuying"
        form is ItemProposalSupplierForm
        save on next
    Questions is a Panel
        valid when (ItemProposalQuestionsExist)
        mouse over text is "PleaseAnswerQuestionsRelatingToNewItemProposals"
        panel header is "PleaseAnswerQuestionsRelatingToNewItemProposals"
        template is ItemProposalQuestionRel
            business class is ResponseToSupplierItemRequestQuestion
                form is ResponseToSupplierItemRequestQuestionForm
